[normal]
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]In rural Indian agricultural households, direct care costs for households with a disabled were as much as three months’ income, and this does not include other indirect costs of care
[normal].  
[normal]
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]A study in Tanzania showed that households with a disabled member have a mean consumption of less than 60% of the average, and include 20% more members than average.  This results in limited household spending power
[normal]. 
